OL,3,CKeir Starmer enters final week as PM
OL,4,Cwith diplomatic blitz in Paris
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will begin what is
OL,7,Fexpected to be his final week as Prime
OL,8,FMinister with a diplomatic blitz as
OL,9,Fhis expected successor Andy Burnham
OL,10,Fwaits to take over.
OL,12,FMr Burnham, the only candidate in
OL,13,FLabour's leadership process, is
OL,14,Fexpected to officially succeed Sir
OL,15,FKeir on Monday July 20.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
