CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783900129
OL,3,CKeir Starmer enters final week as PM
OL,4,Cwith diplomatic blitz in Paris
OL,6,FNo other challenger can get the
OL,7,Frequired 81 MPs needed to stand
OL,8,Fagainst Mr Burnham, as he has the
OL,9,Fsupport of 322 out of Labour's 403
OL,10,FMPs, and more are likely to nominate
OL,11,Fhim on Monday when they return to
OL,12,FWestminster.
OL,14,FSir Keir will travel to Paris on
OL,15,FMonday where he will join allies of
OL,16,FUkraine for a meeting of the
OL,17,F"coalition of the willing".
OL,19,FHe is also expected to join Bastille
OL,20,FDay events on Tuesday.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@ZO]
