OL,3,CKeir Starmer enters final week as PM
OL,4,Cwith diplomatic blitz in Paris
OL,6,FElsewhere, Rachel Reeves is carrying
OL,7,Fout her final duties as Chancellor and
OL,8,Fis due to give her final Mansion House
OL,9,Fspeech to the City on Tuesday, where
OL,10,Fshe will lay out plans to support
OL,11,Fsmall businesses.
OL,13,FOn Sunday, Ms Reeves warned Mr Burnham
OL,14,Fthat he must remain "laser focused" on
OL,15,Fwhat he wants to achieve in power.
OL,26,@vD@UOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
