CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783900129
OL,3,CKeir Starmer enters final week as PM
OL,4,Cwith diplomatic blitz in Paris
OL,6,FSpeaking to the BBC's Sunday With
OL,7,FLaura Kuenssberg, she said: "It is
OL,8,Fimportant that when Andy walks through
OL,9,Fthat door, that he has a worked-
OL,10,Fthrough plan, because governing is
OL,11,Fhard in Britain, and lots of lots of
OL,12,Fchallenges and shocks will come his
OL,13,Fway.
OL,26,@oD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
