OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783900129
OL,3,CKeir Starmer enters final week as PM
OL,4,Cwith diplomatic blitz in Paris
OL,6,F"What is really important is that him
OL,7,Fand his team are really clear about
OL,8,Fwhat they want to achieve. As those
OL,9,Fshocks come along, he needs to stay
OL,10,Flaser focused on those things that
OL,11,Fhave always motivated him, have always
OL,12,Fdriven him, and are the reason why he
OL,13,Fwants to lead our great country."
OL,15,FMs Reeves has conceded she will not
OL,16,Fstay on as Mr Burnham's chancellor,
OL,17,Fand said it was "perfectly reasonable"
OL,18,Ffor him to be ambitious when asked
OL,19,Fabout claims he had been plotting a
OL,20,Fbid to enter Downing Street for over a
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@aO]yD@QOUyD@fO]
