OL,3,CKeir Starmer enters final week as PM
OL,4,Cwith diplomatic blitz in Paris
OL,6,FMr Burnham is considering the
OL,7,Fpossibility of an expanded budget in
OL,8,Fthe autumn, according to the Financial
OL,9,FTimes.
OL,11,FThe newspaper said that once installed
OL,12,Fas Labour leader, he is mulling over
OL,13,Fincluding a departmental spending
OL,14,Freview with the autumn fiscal
OL,15,Fstatement, to set out his overall
OL,16,Fstrategy until the next election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
